<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Metavis · Inteligência Organizacional</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Transforme dados estruturais da sua empresa em inteligência organizacional real. Decisões mais rápidas, mais precisas, com menos esforço." />

  <!-- Cloudflare Turnstile -->
  <script src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js" async defer></script>

  <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            petroleo: {
              DEFAULT: '#01192B',
              dark:    '#010f1a',
              light:   '#0d2d45',
              faint:   'rgba(1,25,43,0.6)',
            },
            laranja: {
              DEFAULT: '#EE6D07',
              dark:    '#c95a00',
              light:   '#f28336',
              glow:    'rgba(238,109,7,0.18)',
            },
          },
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ['Aeonik Pro', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
          },
        },
      },
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    /* ===== Aeonik Pro Font Face ===== */
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Regular.ttf') format('truetype'),
           url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Light.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 300; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Medium.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 500; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Bold.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Black.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 900; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }

    @keyframes gradient-shift {
      0%   { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50%  { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }
    .hero-bg {
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #010f1a, #01192B, #071e30, #010c17);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradient-shift 14s ease infinite;
    }

    .card-glow:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(238,109,7,0.2), 0 20px 50px -10px rgba(1,25,43,0.5);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .card-glow { transition: all 0.3s ease; }

    .orange-border { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF6B00, rgba(255,107,0,0.3), #FF6B00); height: 1px; }
    .divider      { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); height: 1px; }

    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease;
    }
    .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .dot-pattern {
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,107,0,0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
    }

    .blur-orb {
      filter: blur(90px);
      opacity: 0.25;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .orange-badge {
      background: rgba(255,107,0,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,0,0.3);
      color: #FF6B00;
    }

    .step-connector {
      position: absolute;
      top: 28px;
      right: -50%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,107,0,0.4), transparent);
    }

    /* Form focus ring laranja */
    .lead-input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #FF6B00;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,107,0,0.15);
    }

    /* Loading state do form */
    .btn-submit-loading {
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    /* Animação do check de sucesso */
    @keyframes pop-in {
      0%   { transform: scale(0.5); opacity: 0; }
      70%  { transform: scale(1.1); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    }
    .success-pop { animation: pop-in 0.4s ease forwards; }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-petroleo-dark text-white font-sans antialiased" style="font-family: 'Aeonik Pro', system-ui, sans-serif;">

  <!-- ========== NAVBAR ========== -->
  <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-petroleo-dark/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">

      <a href="/" class="flex items-center">
        <img src="/images/logos/Metavis%20-%20Logotipo%20-%20Branco.png"
             alt="Metavis"
             style="height: 28px; object-fit: contain;"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline';">
        <span style="display:none;" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Metavis<span class="text-laranja">.</span></span>
      </a>

      <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-10 text-sm text-white/60">
        <a href="#solucao"       class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Solução</a>
        <a href="#como-funciona" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Como funciona</a>
        <a href="#seguranca"     class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Segurança</a>
        <a href="#beneficios"    class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Benefícios</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="/auth/login" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors hidden sm:block">
          Entrar
        </a>
        <a href="#interesse"
           class="text-sm bg-laranja hover:bg-laranja-dark text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-laranja/20">
          Solicitar acesso
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </header>


  <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden">

    <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 dot-pattern"></div>

    <!-- Glass cube decorativo — cobre a tela toda -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none select-none overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/branding/metavis-glass-cube-01.png" alt=""
           style="position:absolute; top:0; right:0; height:100%; width:100%; object-fit:cover; opacity:0.38;"
           draggable="false">
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 w-full">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

        <!-- Texto -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4">
            Sua empresa,<br/>
            <span class="text-laranja">vista por dentro.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-base text-white/65 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
            Transforme dados estruturais da sua organização em inteligência real.
            Identifique padrões, antecipe riscos e tome decisões com base em
            análises profundas.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Formulário Hero -->
        <div id="hero-form-wrapper" class="bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1.5">Solicite acesso antecipado</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mb-4">Preencha abaixo e nossa equipe entra em contato.</p>

          <form id="hero-lead-form" class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-white/70 mb-1.5">Seu nome completo</label>
              <input type="text" name="nome" required placeholder="Ex: João Silva"
                class="lead-input w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/25 transition-all" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-white/70 mb-1.5">Nome da empresa</label>
              <input type="text" name="nome_empresa" required placeholder="Ex: Acme Consultoria"
                class="lead-input w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/25 transition-all" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-white/70 mb-1.5">E-mail corporativo</label>
              <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="voce@empresa.com"
                class="lead-input w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/25 transition-all" />
            </div>

            <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="<%= turnstileSiteKey %>" data-theme="dark"></div>

            <div id="hero-form-error" class="hidden text-sm text-red-400 bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-3"></div>

            <button type="submit" id="hero-submit-btn"
              class="w-full bg-laranja hover:bg-laranja-dark text-white font-bold py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm transition-all shadow-lg shadow-laranja/20 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <span id="hero-btn-text">Solicitar acesso gratuito</span>
              <svg id="hero-spinner" class="hidden animate-spin w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle>
                <path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4z"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>

          </form>

          <!-- Sucesso -->
          <div id="hero-form-success" class="hidden text-center py-6 success-pop">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-laranja/15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Recebemos seu interesse!</h4>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Nossa equipe vai entrar em contato em breve.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-petroleo-dark to-transparent"></div>
  </section>


  <!-- ========== PROBLEMA (transição de cores — sem imagem) ========== -->
  <section id="solucao" class="relative py-16 px-6" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #010f1a 0%, #071825 50%, #0a1e2e 100%);">
    <!-- fade-out embaixo fundindo com a próxima seção -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-40 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #0a1e2e);"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-center mb-10 fade-up">
        <span class="text-laranja text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">O problema</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-3 mb-3 leading-tight">
          Dados existem.<br/>
          <span class="text-white/30">Inteligência, não.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          A maioria das empresas coleta dados sobre pessoas e estrutura organizacional,
          mas não consegue extrair inteligência acionável. O resultado são decisões baseadas
          em intuição — não em evidência.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 fade-up">

        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 card-glow">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Dados dispersos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Informações em planilhas desconectadas que ninguém consegue cruzar de forma confiável.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 card-glow">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Análises lentas</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Gerar um relatório sobre estrutura organizacional leva dias — quando deveria levar minutos.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 card-glow">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-laranja/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Decisões cegas</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Sem visibilidade real, líderes decidem por intuição — e arcam com as consequências.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ========== SOLUÇÃO + COMO FUNCIONA (cube-02 ao fundo das 2 seções) ========== -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background: #0a1e2e;">
    <!-- cube-02 ao fundo -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none select-none">
      <img src="/images/branding/metavis-glass-cube-02.png" alt=""
           style="position:absolute; top:0; left:0; height:100%; width:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position: left center; opacity:0.4;"
           draggable="false">
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#0a1e2e] via-[#0a1e2e]/80 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
    <!-- Gradiente de transição: funde com a seção "O problema" acima -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 pointer-events-none" style="height: 180px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #091d2d 0%, 50%, transparent 100%);"></div>

  <!-- ========== SOLUÇÃO ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-16 px-6 pb-0">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-center mb-8 fade-up">
        <span class="text-laranja text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">A solução</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-3 leading-tight">
          Metavis transforma estrutura<br/>
          em <span class="text-laranja">inteligência</span>.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-up flex justify-end pb-24">
        <div class="space-y-6 max-w-md">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-laranja/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Visão estrutural completa</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Entenda a composição da sua organização: hierarquia, distribuição de papéis e gaps de competência.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-laranja/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Análises por camadas</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Filtre por departamento, senioridade ou cargo. Cada corte revela uma perspectiva diferente.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-laranja/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Inteligência sempre atualizada</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">Novo upload, novos insights imediatos. Sem relatórios manuais, sem espera.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== COMO FUNCIONA ========== -->
  <section id="como-funciona" class="relative py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <div class="text-center mb-10 fade-up">
        <span class="text-laranja text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Processo</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-3 mb-3 leading-tight">
          Da planilha ao insight<br/>em 3 passos.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/45 text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Sem integrações complexas. Sem código. Sem consultores externos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 fade-up">

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 h-full card-glow">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-laranja/15 leading-none">01</span>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-laranja/12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mt-3 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Upload dos dados</h3>
            <p class="text-white/45 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Faça upload da planilha de dados estruturais da sua equipe usando o template padronizado da Metavis. Excel ou CSV, sem fricção.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 -right-4 w-8 text-laranja/30 z-10">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 h-full card-glow">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-laranja/15 leading-none">02</span>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-laranja/12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mt-3 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Processamento automático</h3>
            <p class="text-white/45 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              A Metavis valida, estrutura e processa os dados automaticamente. Nenhuma configuração manual necessária da sua parte.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 -right-4 w-8 text-laranja/30 z-10">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8 rounded-2xl p-6 h-full card-glow">
            <span class="text-5xl font-black text-laranja/15 leading-none">03</span>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-laranja/12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mt-3 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-laranja" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Inteligência disponível</h3>
            <p class="text-white/45 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Acesse análises estruturais profundas, comparativas e projeções — em uma interface clara, acessível a qualquer liderança.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  </div><!-- fim wrapper cube-02 -->


  <!-- ========== SEGURANÇA ========== -->
  <section id="seguranca" class="relative py-16 px-6 bg-petroleo-dark" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a1e2e 0%, #010f1a 12%, #01192B 100%) !important;">
    <!-- fade-out embaixo fundindo com benefícios -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-48 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #0a1e2e);"></div>
